{"lemma":"زُلالِ","slug":"زُلالِ","root":"ز.ل.ل","root_slug":"ز-ل-ل","root_link":"/words/roots/ز-ل-ل","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":false},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":1,"pos_tags":["noun"],"has_etymology":false,"sense_count":3},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n17953"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%B2%D9%8F%D9%84%D8%A7%D9%84%D9%90"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"noun","gloss":"limpid, pure, clear (of water, etc)"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"egg white, albumen"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"albumin"}]},"etymology":null,"ipa":["/zu.laːl/"],"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n17953","headword_ar":"زُلَالٌ","root":"zl","body":[{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A certain animal, of small, white body; which, when it dies, is put into water, and renders it cool,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"cold:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA:) [Golius describes it as"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a worm that is bred in snow;"},{"kind":"text","text":"of which Aristotle speaks in his Hist. Animalium, l. ↓. 19; and he adds, on the authority of Dmr, that it is"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of the length of a finger, generally marked with yellow spots; and swelling in water such as is termed"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mA' AlzlAl","text_ar":"ماء الزلال"},{"kind":"text","text":".] ―         -b2-  Hence, [it is said to be] applied to water, as meaning"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Cool,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"cold:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA:) or, so applied,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"sweet:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"sweet, clear,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"limpid, pure, easy in its descent, that slips into the throat;"},{"kind":"text","text":"as also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"zulaAzilN","text_ar":"زُلَازِلٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":": (TA:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"quick in its descent and passage in the throat,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K, * TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"cool,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"cold, sweet, clear,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"limpid, easy in its descent;"},{"kind":"text","text":"as also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"zaliylN","text_ar":"زَلِيلٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"zaluwlN","text_ar":"زَلُولٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"zulaAzilN","text_ar":"زُلَازِلٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":". (K.) ―         -b3-  And"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Clear,"},{"kind":"text","text":"as applied to anything. (TA.)"}],"source_refs":["TA","S"]}]},"classical_definitions":null}